{"tid":540970,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel《黑豹》16歲妹比Iron Man還要聰明","createTime":"2018-01-26T03:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T12:26:07.000Z","uid":41453,"like":13,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"b6406a5b8146ef5c58667747cea6a6749568414b","tid":540970,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"在 Marvel 日前提早公開的一段電影片段中，黑豹 T&rsquo;Challa 的妹妹 Shuri（Letitia Wright 飾）展示了她對 Wakanda 高科技的掌握與了解程度，而與此同時，《黑豹》電影製作人 Nate Moore 近日也向 Screen Rant，透露了更多有關 Shuri 這角色的背景設定：<br />\n<br />\nAs far as the technologically-advanced side, in our mind, and in our incarnation, Shuri is the head of the Wakanda Design Group. She&rsquo;s the smartest person in the world, smarter than Tony Stark but she&rsquo;s a sixteen-year-old girl which we thought was really interesting.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNate Moore 表示 Shuri 領導著 Wakanda 的設計團隊，這解釋了為何她對 Wakanda 的高科技如此了解，而且只有 16 歲的她是 Marvel 電影世界中最聰明的人，甚至比 Tony Stark 更加聰明。由此可大概估計到，這位 Wakanda 公主是黑豹 T&rsquo;Challa 以外，電影故事中的另一位核心人物，她掌握著 T&rsquo;Challa 應付敵人的強大武器，相信無論是在上映在即的《黑豹》，還是在往後的《Avengers：Infinity War》中，Shuri 都會對劇情發展帶來重要影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/1/black-panther-sister-shuri-smarter-tony-stark\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F1%2Fblack-panther-sister-shuri-smarter-tony-stark&d=QRFx0Pw9SOxgqvOnL0RsbgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b6ca8aee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/1/black-panther-sister-shuri-smarter-tony-stark</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/114208_8c9cfdc3c278f59985a6115a7411961e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F114208_8c9cfdc3c278f59985a6115a7411961e.jpg&h=79cd96cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7045fda4c03ad888a26dddf2652fd878970c4d83","tid":540970,"uid":11962,"like":117,"dislike":13,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:43:44.000Z","ms